{"tid":2342562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭也倒米：銅芯口罩麻麻哋","createTime":"2020-12-27T08:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T10:13:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2e53daf79b7830612482e77fbdeb66cb9d388a","tid":2342562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Jj53tUkfVfe1Aga77FEO1g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni40/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/pTXdKrn.O64ijicJC6H_yQ--~B/aD00Mjk7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/3c6f9ee5a979f5cd4346ce4ed490f050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJj53tUkfVfe1Aga77FEO1g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni40%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpTXdKrn.O64ijicJC6H_yQ--~B%2FaD00Mjk7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F3c6f9ee5a979f5cd4346ce4ed490f050&h=484015a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】新冠肺炎爆發初期，市面上「一罩難求」，政府被批評抗疫不力，至年中推出可重用的「銅芯口罩」，雖然曾兩度免費派發給合資格的市民，但劣評如潮，早前有報道指口罩經過清洗後，防菌功能只剩下四成，政府方面更曾親口承認，口罩未必受市民歡迎或接受，就連理應帶頭支持自家出品的特首林鄭月娥也曾「倒自己米」，出席記者會時表示口罩「麻麻哋」。<br />\n<br />\n官員寧戴外科口罩<br />\n<br />\n銅芯口罩一人至少有一個，但查看過往紀錄，就連官員都不肯用。其中林鄭和一眾司局長在5月中出席記者會和立法會會議，均未有佩戴「銅芯抗疫口罩」，只是以外科口罩代替。<br />\n<br />\n特首戴到露出鼻孔<br />\n<br />\n而林鄭在6月中出席行政會議前的例行記者會時，口罩戴得不夠穩固，曾兩度露出鼻孔，期間她更忍不住發言指「今日個口罩麻麻哋，可能洗得多鬆咗啦」，難免令人質疑銅芯口罩的實質效用。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，林鄭佩戴銅芯口罩出現「甩轆」場面不止一次，她9月初出席行會前見記者期間，過程中最少兩次用手調整口罩位置，而右耳亦未能正確穿戴口罩，更着一眾攝影記者「唔好係咁影佢」，並表示「可能個口罩緊得滯」，繼而除下口罩。她雖然一度嘗試戴回口罩但不成功，再詢問一旁人員有否另一個替換，擾攘一會兒後選擇直接除下口罩發言，更指與記者有保持1.5米距離，應該無問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/林鄭也倒米-銅芯口罩麻麻哋-214500536.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E4%B9%9F%E5%80%92%E7%B1%B3-%E9%8A%85%E8%8A%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%BA%BB%E9%BA%BB%E5%93%8B-214500536.html&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=d5bcfa3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/林鄭也倒米-銅芯口罩麻麻哋-214500536.html</a>"},{"pid":"17179691b2ea41c5dd73ded7e6ae74cea64c0467","tid":2342562,"uid":36178,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:30:32.000Z","msg":"可能屌得多鬆咗啦"},{"pid":"73818cd327748c7460655e476afb821bae00842b","tid":2342562,"uid":37666,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"2億公帑造垃圾"},{"pid":"6f737f206cf3406210ed67e2484f6da5223665cb","tid":2342562,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"而家供應都穩定啦<br />\n係啲環保撚多事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0058ff275bd48a368998cfcabbeef88cf53b1d14","tid":2342562,"uid":92448,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"公司同事日日都戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa95691e6ff6e58cb8f72ed4b03ce6f8f84a5ff","tid":2342562,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:39:26.000Z","msg":"都已經送撚左2億比自己友炒樓，之後梗係關人撚事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e122578dac7d0df404d5b7d86eec1bba8408ad12","tid":2342562,"uid":209126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0058ff275bd48a368998cfcabbeef88cf53b1d14","tid":2342562,"uid":92448,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"公司同事日日都戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4732e7fc19e482365fdfb358357313cb2612cd10","tid":2342562,"uid":24243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"除咗對港共表忠之外, 呢隻垃圾罩根本冇用"},{"pid":"4e1548